{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol"},"metadata":{"title":"TestDBusProtocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TestDBusProtocol"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"TestDBusProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO16TestDBusProtocolP","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"protocol","roleHeading":"Protocol"},"topicSections":[{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/busAddress","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/flags","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/test_dbus_ptr-399n4"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"anchor":"Instance-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/addServiceDir(path:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/bind(property:to:_:flags:transformFrom:transformTo:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/down()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/get(property:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/getBusAddress()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/getFlags()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/set(property:value:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/stop()","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/up()"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"TestDBusProtocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","text":"ObjectProtocol","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that "},{"code":"GTestDBus","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" modifies the user’s environment, calling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"man:setenv(3)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". This is not thread-safe, so all "},{"code":"GTestDBus","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calls should be completed before threads are spawned, or should have"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"appropriate locking to ensure no access conflicts to environment variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"shared between ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GTestDBus"},{"text":" and other threads.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Creating-unit-tests-using-GTestDBus","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Creating unit tests using `GTestDBus`"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Testing of D-Bus services can be tricky because normally we only ever run"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"D-Bus services over an existing instance of the D-Bus daemon thus we"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"usually don’t activate D-Bus services that are not yet installed into the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"target system. The "},{"code":"GTestDBus","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" object makes this easier for us by taking care"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the lower level tasks such as running a private D-Bus daemon and looking"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"up uninstalled services in customizable locations, typically in your source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"code tree."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first thing you will need is a separate service description file for the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"D-Bus daemon. Typically a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"services"},{"type":"text","text":" subdirectory of your "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"tests"},{"text":" directory","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is a good place to put this file."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The service file should list your service along with an absolute path to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"uninstalled service executable in your source tree. Using autotools we would","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"achieve this by adding a file such as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"my-server.service.in"},{"text":" in the services","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directory and have it processed by configure.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["[D-BUS Service]","Name=org.gtk.GDBus.Examples.ObjectManager","Exec=`abs_top_builddir`@\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-example-objectmanager-server"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will also need to indicate this service directory in your test"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"fixtures, so you will need to pass the path while compiling your","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"test cases. Typically this is done with autotools with an added","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"preprocessor flag specified to compile your tests such as:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["-DTEST_SERVICES=\\\"\"$(abs_top_builddir)\/tests\/services\"\\\""]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once you have a service definition file which is local to your source tree,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"you can proceed to set up a GTest fixture using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GTestDBus"},{"type":"text","text":" scaffolding."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An example of a test fixture for D-Bus services can be found"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"here:"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/gitlab.gnome.org\/GNOME\/glib\/-\/blob\/HEAD\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-test-fixture.c","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that these examples only deal with isolating the D-Bus aspect of your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"service. To successfully run isolated unit tests on your service you may need","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"some additional modifications to your test case fixture. For example; if your"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"service uses [class"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Settings"},{"text":"] and installs a schema then it is important","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that your test service not load the schema in the ordinary installed location"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(chances are that your service and schema files are not yet installed, or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"worse; there is an older version of the schema file sitting in the install"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"location).","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Most of the time we can work around these obstacles using the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"environment. Since the environment is inherited by the D-Bus daemon"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"created by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GTestDBus"},{"type":"text","text":" and then in turn inherited by any services the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"D-Bus daemon activates, using the setup routine for your fixture is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a practical place to help sandbox your runtime environment. For the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"rather typical GSettings case we can work around this by setting","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GSETTINGS_SCHEMA_DIR"},{"type":"text","text":" to the in tree directory holding your schemas"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the above "},{"code":"fixture_setup()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" routine.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The GSettings schemas need to be locally pre-compiled for this to work. This","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can be achieved by compiling the schemas locally as a step before running"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"test cases, an autotools setup might do the following in the directory"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"holding schemas:"}]},{"syntax":null,"code":["    all-am:","            $(GLIB_COMPILE_SCHEMAS) .","","    CLEANFILES += gschemas.compiled"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol exposes the methods and properties of an underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GTestDBus"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The default implementation of these can be found in the protocol extension below."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"For a concrete class that implements these methods and properties, see "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBus"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Alternatively, use "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusRef"},{"text":" as a lighweight, ","type":"text"},{"code":"unowned","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reference if you already have an instance you just want to use.","type":"text"}]}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP"],"type":"inheritsFrom"},{"title":"Conforming Types","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBus","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusRef"],"type":"conformingTypes"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A helper class for testing code which uses D-Bus without touching the user’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"session bus."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/testdbusprotocol"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GIO/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","title":"GLibObject.ObjectProtocol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/TestDBusProtocol/flags":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TestDBusFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO13TestDBusFlagsV"}],"type":"topic","title":"flags","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusFlags","isActive":true},{"text":" specifying the behaviour of the D-Bus session.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/testdbusprotocol\/flags","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/TestDBusProtocol\/flags"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/TestDBusProtocol/set(property:value:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"set(property:value:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"property","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3